{"title_page": "6th Lux Style Awards", "text_new": "{{unreferenced|date=February 2013}}\n{{Infobox film awards\n| number              = 6\n| award               = Lux Style Awards\n| award_link          = Lux Style Awards\n| type                = \n| image               = \n| image_size = 200px\n| caption             = \n| date                = \n| site                = [[Malaysia]]\n| host                = \n| producer            = \n| director            = \n| organizer           = \n| best_picture        = \n| best_actor_film     = \n| best_actor          = \n| best_actress_film   = \n| best_actress        = \n| channel             = [[ARY Digital]]\n| network             = \n| duration            = \n| ratings             = \n| last                = 5th\n| next                = 7th\n}}\n\nThe '''6th [[Lux Style Awards]]''' ceremony was held in [[Malaysia]]. The show was hosted by [[Sana Nawaz]], [[Shoaib Mansoor]] and from the members of [[Banana News Network]].\n==Film==\n{| class=\"wikitable style\"\n! Category \n! Winner\n|-\n| Best Film\n| [[Majajan]]\n|-\n| Best Film Director\n| [[Syed Noor]]-[[Majajan]]\n|-\n| Best Film Actor\n| [[Shaan Shahid|Shaan]]-[[Majajan]]\n|-\n| Best Film Actress\n| [[Saima Noor]]-[[Majajan]]\n|}\n\n==Television==\n{| class=\"wikitable style\"\n! Category \n! Winner\n! Nominations \n|-\n| Best TV Play (Terrestrial)\n| Kath Putli-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n|\n* Malangi-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n* Sadoori-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n* Gharoor-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n* Gul Bashra-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n|-\n| Best TV Director (Terrestrial)\n| Sajjad Ahmed-Gul Bashra-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n|\n* Kazim Pasha-Kath Putli-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n* Ataullah Balouch-Sadoori-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n* Tahir-Gharoor-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n* Shahid Zahoor-Malangi-[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\