r|first=Karen|title=Baedeker India|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=bGgf_LkeG2kC&pg=PA284|year=2012|publisher=Baedeker|isbn=978-3-8297-6622-7|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Shackley|first=Myra|title=Managing Sacred Sites: Service Provision and Visitor Experience|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=F18-QxgyHIEC&pg=PA121|year=2001|publisher=Cengage Learning EMEA|isbn=978-1-84480-107-7|ref=}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Sharma|first1=Urmila|last2=Sharma|first2=S.K.|title=Indian Political Thought|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BX3wIjJ9mvMC&pg=PA197|year=2001|publisher=Atlantic Publishers & Dist|isbn=978-81-7156-678-5|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Sharma|first=Virendra Nath|title=Sawai Jai Singh And His Astronomy|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QRA2mgZnXXMC&pg=PA191|year=1995|publisher=Motilal Banarsidass|isbn=978-81-208-1256-7|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Singh|first=Ram Bali|title=Rajput Clan-settlements in Varanasi District|year=1975|publisher= National Geographical Society of India|oclc=4702795|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last= Singh |first=Rana |title=Banaras: Making of India's Heritage City|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JwMaBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA54|date=2 October 2009|publisher=Cambridge Scholars Publishing|isbn=978-1-4438-1579-6|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Singh|first2=Pravin S.|last2=Rana|title=Banaras region: a spiritual & cultural guide|year=2002|publisher=Indica Books|isbn=9788186569245|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Singh|first=Sarina|title=India|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vK88ktao7pIC&pg=PA453|year=2009|publisher=Lonely Planet|isbn=978-1-74179-151-8|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|title=The Small Hands of Slavery: Bonded Child Labor in India|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NfX3sRoJ3rYC|year=1996|publisher=[[Human Rights Watch]]| ref = {{harvid|Human Rights Watch|1996}}|isbn=978-1-56432-172-5}}\n* {{cite book|last=Tiwari|first=Reena|title=Space-Body-Ritual: Performativity in the City|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=P7W1I4j75E8C&pg=PA47|year=2010|publisher=Lexington Books|isbn=978-0-7391-2857-2|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Twain |first=Mark |authorlink=Mark Twain |title=Following the Equator: A journey around the world |url=http://www.literaturecollection.com/a/twain/following-equator/ |year=1897 |publisher=Hartford, Connecticut, American Pub. Co. |isbn=0-404-01577-8 |oclc=577051 |chapter=L |chapterurl=http://www.literaturecollection.com/a/twain/following-equator/51/ |ref=harv |access-date=7 February 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080228225229/http://www.literaturecollection.com/a/twain/following-equator/ |archive-date=28 February 2008 |url-status=dead  }}\n* {{cite book|last=Vera|first=Zak|title=Invisible River: Sir Richard's Last Mission|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8HhVcspIBU4C&pg=PA179|year=2010|publisher=AuthorHouse|isbn=978-1-4389-0020-9|ref=}}{{sps|date=February 2020}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Wilder-Smith|first1=Annelies|last2=Shaw|first2=Marc|last3=Schwartz|first3=Eli|title=Travel Medicine: Tales Behind the Science|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=itegkZspCgUC&pg=PA273|year=2012|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-0-08-045359-0|ref=}}\n* {{cite book|last= Sukul |first=Kuber Nath |title=Varanasi Down The Ages|url=http://books.groogle.com/BOOKS?ID=Y2LUAAAAMAAJ|year=1974|publisher=Kameshwar Nath Sukul|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last= Warikoo |first=K. |title=Religion and Security in South and Central Asia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0zRZBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA192|date=1 November 2010|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-136-89020-8|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite encyclopedia|last=Wood|first=Jolie M.F.|title=Contentious politics and civil society in Varanasi|encyclopedia=Re-framing Democracy and Agency at India: Interrogating Political Society|year=2011|publisher=Anthem Press|isbn=978-0-85728-350-4|editor=Ajay Gudavarthy|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last= Vit-Suzan |first=Dr Ilan |title=Architectural Heritage Revisited: A Holistic Engagement of its Tangible and Intangible Constituents|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TKv8AgAAQBAJ&pg=PR11|date=28 March 2014|publisher=Ashgate Publishing, Ltd.|isbn=978-1-4724-2064-0|ref=harv}}\n{{div col end}}\n{{refend}}\n\n== Further reading ==\n* {{cite book|last1=Banks|first1=Marcus|last2=Morphy|first2=Howard|title=Rethinking Visual Anthropology|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mfddjqZGZygC|year=1999|publisher=Yale University Press|isbn=978-0-300-07854-1}}\n* {{cite book|last=Kara|first=Siddharth|title=Sex Trafficking: Inside the Business of Modern Slavery|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LL4kfg6CPuwC&pg=PA59|year=2010|publisher=Columbia University Press|isbn=978-0-231-13961-8}}\n* {{cite book|last=Mukherjee|first=Neela|title=Alternative Perspectives on Livelihood, Agriculture and Air Pollution|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ymo-TP_DhTIC&pg=PA49|year=2002|publisher=Concept Publishing Company|isbn=978-81-7022-986-5}}\n* {{cite book|last=Partridge|first=Christopher Hugh|title=Introduction to World Religions|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7lEFyGiP5r8C|year=2005|publisher=Fortress Press|isbn=978-0-8006-3714-9}}\n* {{cite book|last= Shetty |first=Rekha |title=Innovation Sutra: The Secret of Good Business and a Good Life|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=a6JQAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT73|date=1 May 2014|publisher=Penguin Books Limited|isbn=978-93-5118-696-0|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|author=Singh|title=Longman Panorama History 7|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=URW9LABgF_4C&pg=PA73|year=2007|publisher=Pearson Education India|isbn=978-81-317-1175-0}}\n* {{cite book|last=Trayler|first=Richard|title=Life Is Short...Compared to Eternity|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2mzsNsjVi1gC&pg=PA182|year=2010|publisher=Xulon Press|isbn=978-1-61215-343-8}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Wikiquote}}\n{{Commons category|Varanasi}}\n{{Wikivoyage}}\n{{Wikiversity|The Varanasi Heritage Dossier}}\n* [http://varanasi.nic.in/ Official website of Varanasi District]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20090908004947/http://www.up-tourism.com/destination/varanasi/varanasi.htm State Government Tourism Website]\n* {{curlie|Regional/Asia/India/Uttar_Pradesh/Localities/Varanasi}}\n* [http://www.sai.uni-heidelberg.de/abt/IND/publikation/bibbanaras/bibbanaras.php Banaras Bibliography] at the S\u00fcdasien-Institut, [[Heidelberg University]]\n\n{{Geographic location\n|North     = [[Azamgarh]]\n|Northeast = [[Ghazipur]]\n|West      = [[Sant Ravidas Nagar]]\n|Northwest = [[Jaunpur, Uttar Pradesh|Jaunpur]]\n|Center    = Varanasi\n|South     = [[Mirzapur]]\n|Southwest = [[Chunar]]\n|Southeast = [[Chakia, Uttar Pradesh|Chakia]]\n|East      = [[Chandauli]]\n|\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|list =\n{{Hindu holy cities}}\n{{Ancient Dharmic centres of Higher Learning}}\n{{Varanasi district}}\n{{Varanasi division topics}}\n{{Million-plus agglomerations in India}}\n{{Uttar Pradesh}}\n\n}}\n{{Varanasi}}\n{{Hinduism (compact)}}\n{{Shaivism}}\n{{Good article}}\n\n[[Category:Varanasi| ]]<!-- please leave the empty space as standard -->\n[[Category:Ancient Indian cities]]\n[[Category:Buddhist pilgrimage sites in India]]\n[[Category:Census towns in Uttar Pradesh]]\n[[Category:Census towns in Uttar Pradesh by district]]\n[[Category:Census towns in Varanasi district]]\n[[Category:Villages in Varanasi district]]\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Varanasi district]]\n[[Category:Hindu holy cities]]\n[[Category:Holy cities]]\n[[Category:Populated places established in the 2nd millennium BC]]\n[[Category:Former capital cities in India]]\n[[Category:Cities in Uttar Pradesh]]\n", "text_old": "{{Distinguish |Varanasi division|Varanasi district|Varanasi Tehsil}}\n{{redirect|Banaras}}\n{{pp|small=yes}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2019}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                            = Varanasi\n| native_name                     = <!-- Please do not add any Indic script in this infobox, per WP:INDICSCRIPT policy. -->\n| other_name                      = Kashi<br />Banara